
ADÉSTO supplicatiónibus nostris, omnípotens Deus: et, quibus fidúciam sperándæ pietátis indúlges, intercedénte beáto Augustíno Confessóre tuo atque Pontífice consuétæ misericórdiæ tríbue benígnus efféctum. Per Dóminum.
GIVE ear, O almighty God, to our supplications, and grant that we, whom thou dost benignly encourage to hope in thy lovingkindness, may, by the intercession of blessed Augustine thy Confessor and Bishop, experience the effect of thy wonted mercy. Through our Lord.
